WEBVTT

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:32.720
For years we have been dreaming
of such personal bots,

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.120
now they are a reality.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:38.400
They will make us free
from day to day problems.

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:42.240
So now imagine a world with these bots.

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:46.920
In that world everything 
will be connected to the internet,

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.160
connected to each other,

00:01:49.160 --> 00:01:50.240
connected to you.

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:54.760
We call this Internet of Things, or IOT.

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:57.280
Your car,

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:59.360
your fridge, television,

